Gracias
My download Laungaue files needed to be burned or mounted  (with alcocol or simular) using the ISO (or other format).

Everybody, if you did everything right and you are getting an error "The Language CD was not found to install", check to see if the version of the application you have will work with your particular language. Some languages are not compatible with version 3. For instance I tried to install Thai, and finally learned from the rosettastone website that it only works with version 2 of the application!
